---
title: Sesame Turkey and Broccoli Noodles with Carrots and Green Onions
description: Sometimes you're just craving a big bowl of noodles, and we've got you covered! Nutty sesame oil makes this turkey and broccoli noodle dish wonderfully aromatic, and all the usual suspects build deep flavour: hoisin sauce, soy sauce, garlic, and more. Tonight, spaghetti takes the place of noodles; a swap you never knew you'd love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nouilles-au-brocoli-et-a-la-dinde-au-sesame-99238a0c.jpg
